Audit technique complet avec solutions:

### 1. Configuration Robots & Sitemap

**robots.txt optimisé :**
```txt
User-agent: *
Allow: /
Disallow: /api/
Disallow: /admin/

Sitemap: https://{{ url }}/sitemap.xml
```

**Génération sitemap dynamique :**
```javascript
// scripts/generate-sitemap.js
import { SitemapStream, streamToPromise } from 'sitemap'
import { createWriteStream } from 'fs'

const sitemap = new SitemapStream({ hostname: 'https://{{ url }}' })

const pages = [
  { url: '/', changefreq: 'daily', priority: 1.0 },
  { url: '/about', changefreq: 'monthly', priority: 0.8 }
]

pages.forEach(page => sitemap.write(page))
sitemap.end()
```

### 2. Implémentation Schema.org

```vue
<script setup>
import { useSchemaOrg } from '@unhead/schema-org'

useSchemaOrg([
  {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: 'Nom de l\'entreprise',
    logo: 'https://example.com/logo.png',
    url: 'https://example.com'
  },
  {
    '@type': 'WebSite',
    name: 'Nom du site',
    url: 'https://example.com'
  }
])
</script>
```

